'''弗朗西斯堡-國際瀑布城國際大橋'''（{{lang-en|Fort Frances–International Falls International Bridge}}）是一條連接[[加拿大|加拿大]]與[[美國|美國]]的國際橋樑，跨越[[雷尼河|雷尼河]]連接南端美國[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]][[國際瀑布城|國際瀑布城]]和北端加拿大[[安大略省|安大略省]][[弗朗西斯堡|弗朗西斯堡]]，由美國紙業公司波伊西（{{lang|en|Boise Inc.}}）旗下的明尼蘇達、達科他和西部鐵路公司（{{lang|en|Minnesota, Dakota and Western Railway}}，簡稱MD&W）和加拿大紙業公司堅毅林木產品（{{lang|en|Resolute Forest Products}}）共同擁有<ref>{{cite web |author=Liala Helal |url=http://www.ifallsjournal.com/news/business_news/border-service-owners-of-international-bridge-report-increased-crossings-into/article_02c4d53a-6a22-11e1-b54a-001a4bcf6878.html |title=Border service, owners of International Bridge report increased crossings into Canada |publisher=''The Journal'' (International Falls) |date=2012-03-10 |accessdate=2014-03-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Duane Hicks |url=http://www.fftimes.com/node/252310 |title=Bridge, Customs celebration in the works |publisher=''Fort Frances Times'' |date=2012-06-12 |accessdate=2014-03-20 |archive-date=2014-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321010401/http://www.fftimes.com/node/252310 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，年度汽車流量近90萬架次<ref name="MPR"/>。

大橋供鐵路和汽車行駛：鐵路軌坐落大橋的西側，而東側則載有來回方向各一條行車線。由於大橋的西側可承受較大的負荷，貨車或巴士等重型車輛亦取道西側過橋。此外，大橋亦承載一條連接兩岸造紙工廠的管道。大橋南行方向無需繳費，北行方向私家車收費為6.00美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ezbordercrossing.com/travel-resources/international-bridge-tolls/international-falls-bridge-toll/#.Uytb8pWPLIU |title=International Falls Bridge Toll |publisher=ezbordercrossing.com |accessdate=2014-03-20 |archive-date=2014-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321012144/http://www.ezbordercrossing.com/travel-resources/international-bridge-tolls/international-falls-bridge-toll/#.Uytb8pWPLIU |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，當地商戶亦有出售折扣儲值卡，憑卡可享用約0.80美元的橋費過橋12次<ref name="MPR">{{cite web |author=Tom Robertson |url=http://www.mprnews.org/story/2006/04/13/bridgesale |title=Border towns want state, province to purchase International Bridge |publisher=MPR News |date=2006-05-17 |accessdate=2014-03-20 |archive-date=2014-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321011222/http://www.mprnews.org/story/2006/04/13/bridgesale |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

大橋於1908年動工，1912年啓用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ifallschamber.com/international-falls-history/ |title=International Falls History |publisher=International Falls Area Chamber of Commerce |accessdate=2014-03-20 |archive-date=2014-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321021855/http://ifallschamber.com/international-falls-history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大橋北端駁上安大略11號和71號省道，兩者皆隸屬[[橫加公路|橫加公路]]；南端則駁上美國53號和71號國道。

